Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:41.70,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}回到自己的心田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:49.38,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}和伙伴们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:55.71,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}上阵浴血奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:14:08.76,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}名誉和荣耀是我们的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:15.02,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}去受伤 去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:21.96,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}最终长眠于此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:28.19,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}维杰啊 维杰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:35.09,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}我们是生存于大公旗下的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:41.16,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}维杰啊 维杰
